CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 18, 1961, pg. A14 reads: "Kappa Karnival Guests got a real bang out of the party held at the Anchorage, last Friday night. In this picture are guests of Kappa Brother Ralph Barnett and Mrs. Barnett.  Their guests included Mrs. Betty Matthews, Mrs. Guy Kemp, Mr. and Mrs. Harris, Mr. and Mrs. John Trent, Mr. and Mrs. LaVerne Mills, Mr. and Mrs. Fred Clark and Mr. and Mrs. Edward Bailey. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Kappa Alpha Psi's "Kappa Karnival" guests, including Lucell and Betty Matthews on left, Mr. and Mrs. Ralph Barnett, Mrs. Guy Kemp, Mr. and Mrs. Harris, Mr. and Mrs. John Trent, Mr. and Mrs. LaVerne Mills, Mr. and Mrs. Fred Clark and Mr. and Mrs. Edward Bailey, seated around banquet tables in the Anchorage
